column5: I am not sure what to say about this...
American ingenuity. The best in the World bar none.
The only thing that could of made it better if it was a topless Sheila driving it... LOL
If you replace the barbeque with a tackle box, it would make a compact fishing boat.  And you wouldn't have to worry about a ending up with a lap full hot coals after running over someone's wake.
I really hope that's special effects smoke.
It does look at lot like dry ice.
Don’t let misfish see that.  They sole his patented fish and cook.
